# Reproducible code

```{r}
PATH <- "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/aldosolari/SL3/main/docs/"
train = read.csv2(paste0(PATH,"PI_LOW_train.txt"))
test = read.csv2(paste0(PATH,"PI_LOW_test.txt"))
model = lm( y~. , train)
PI = predict(model, newdata = test, interval = "prediction")[,-1]
head(PI)
```
